<D>__{no, she's...}
<A>__{he pulls off a yellow post it note stuck to the computer. it reads: "coffee made. don't touch my computer. back in 10." unseen on the computer screen beside him, the name "margaret barnell" pops up, along with all her pertinent information like pet's name, husband, delusions...}
<C>__{ted }
<D>__{she'll be back in a few minutes. you want to try later?}
